  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-commodity\">supremely powerful</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Life Support System</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>The module is flexible, and exact upgrade statistics are <span class=\"name name-special\">unknown</span> until installation is complete.<br><br>Potentially increases <span class=\"name name-stellar\">life support power</span> and may offer limited <span class=\"name name-stellar\">solar-energy power-offsetting</span>, decreasing power use during daylight.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">维生系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">至强</span>提升。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>开始<VAL_ON>安装升级<>。<br><br>该模块很灵活，具体升级信息在安装结束前<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提升<span class=\"name name-stellar\">维生系统能量</span>，同时可能提供有限的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太阳能能量补充</span>，能减少日光下的能量消耗。",
    "TencentChinese": "对<span class=\"name name-technology\">维生系统</span>的<span class=\"name name-commodity\">至强</span>提升。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>开始安装升级。<br><br>增加<span class=\"name name-stellar\">维生系统能量</span>并提供有限的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太阳能能量补充</span>，能减少日光下的能量消耗。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-commodity\">維生系統</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">最強大</span>升級。用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此模組富有彈性，直到安裝完成前，確切的升級數據為<span class=\"name name-special\">未知</span>。<br><br>可能提高<span class=\"name name-stellar\">維生系統能量</span>並且可提供有限的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太陽能功率補償</span>，並減少白天的能源消耗。"
